payload: [{"qId": 1001, "answer": "Haan, humare store pe Snickers, Mars Bar aur Twix available hain."}, {"qId": 1002, "answer": "Snickers sabse zyada bikta hai, aur mai khud bhi aksar Bounty leta hoon."}, {"qId": 1003, "answer": "Filhaal Mars Bar ki demand zyada hai, kyunki uspe achha discount chal raha hai."}, {"qId": 1004, "answer": "Haan, jab scheme milti hai toh sales badhti hai, kyunki log discount dekh ke zyada kharidte hain."}, {"qId": 1005, "answer": "Haan, naye products try karne ka shauk hota hai customers ko, lekin agar koi achha offer ho toh aur bhi zyada interest dikhate hain."}]
